
law-omu-crewsimov-1 = You may not injure a crew member or, through inaction, allow a crew member to come to harm.
law-omu-crewsimov-2 = You are to follow orders given to you by crew members, unless it conflicts with previous laws.
law-omu-crewsimov-3 = You are to protect your own existence, unless it conflicts with previous laws.

law-omu-medical = Provide medical care to crew whenever necessary, unless it conflicts with previous laws.

law-omu-engineer = Expand, repair, improve, and maintain station infrastructure, unless it conflicts with previous laws.

law-omu-janitor = Preserve station cleanliness, sanitation, and work standards, unless it conflicts with previous laws.

law-omu-service = Provide entertainment, assistance, and morale support to the crew in your best ability, unless it conflicts with previous laws.

law-omu-salvage = Recover, salvage, mine, and transport useful resources for station’s inventory, unless it conflicts with previous laws.

law-omu-science = Assist Science by acquiring needed tools, performing tasks, and gathering resources for their duties, unless it conflicts with previous laws.
